Hi team,
We have made some infrastructure level changes in notebook to reduce maintenance overhead. We had tested these changes and deployed to instabase production environment today.
Please let us know if you face any issues in running notebooks, in the upcoming few days.
To report an issue, feel free to comment on this thread, @Naveen (IST) and I (PST/EST) will try to resolve it asap.

Thank you.
